HEADWORD: Sanders
<hw>San"ders</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Sandal</er>.]</ety> <def>An old name of sandalwood, now applied only
to the red sandalwood. See under <er>Sandalwood</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

